title: Start
body:
<<setSpeakerName DialogueSwitcher Me>>
Hmmm.
I could sure go for coffee.
And I want Starbucks, specifically. Not the way more economical one at work.
I should also get a haircut.
<<setSpeakerName DialogueSwitcher Dan>>
Oh my god Won, stop talking to yourself out loud. Some of us are trying to work.
<<setSpeakerName DialogueSwitcher Me>>
Hey, what did they do with that water cooler anyway?
<<setSpeakerName DialogueSwitcher Dan>>
They got rid of it.
Seeing as how we have fountains all over the campus.
<<PlayFinalCard Canvas>>
